        "TileImage": "$($repository b13314ab-ea25-48b7-9e51-8ebb87788e20).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning, 47. Your targets are wealthy Texan businessman Amos Dexter, and former CEO of Quantum Leap Jason Portman. According to our clients, Dexter is set to be the next heir to the controversial Dexter Industries and Portman has plans to secretly drain Quantum Leap funds. Both targets are patients at the GAMA Private Hospital at Hokkaido, Japan for a lung transplant and facial reconstruction respectively and our clients would prefer if they never check out. Best of luck, 47.",
